WEBVTT

00:00:27.207 --> 00:00:34.132
(Applause)

00:00:39.592 --> 00:00:43.166
Bhakti Sharma: Imagine,
in the scorching Rajasthan heat,

00:00:43.190 --> 00:00:45.127
on a hot summer afternoon,

00:00:45.151 --> 00:00:48.928
a two-and-a-half-year-old
riding on a moped behind her mom,

00:00:48.952 --> 00:00:51.119
not knowing where they were headed.

00:00:51.143 --> 00:00:52.839
And 20 minutes later,

00:00:52.863 --> 00:00:55.324
that two-and-a-half-year-old finds herself

00:00:55.348 --> 00:00:57.712
completely submerged in water.

00:00:58.093 --> 00:00:59.299
Before I knew it,

00:00:59.323 --> 00:01:02.077
I would be kicking, splashing, screaming,